!!!  
%html.no-js
  %head
    %meta{:charset=>"utf-8"}
    %meta{"http-equiv"=> "X-UA-Compatible", :content=>"IE=edge,chrome=1"}
    %title Oahu. connect with your audience, anywhere.
    %meta{:name=>"author", :content=>"Oahu"}
    %meta{:viewport=>"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"}
    %link{:rel=>"shortcut icon", :href=>"/favicon.ico"}
    %link{:rel=>"apple-touch-icon", :href=>"/apple-touch-icon.png"}
    %meta{:name=>"viewport", :content=>"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"}

    %link{:rel => "stylesheet", :href=> "/assets/vendor/bootstrap/bootstrap.min.css" }
    %link{:rel => "stylesheet", :href=> "/assets/vendor/bootstrap/bootstrap-responsive.min.css" }
    %link{:rel => "stylesheet", :href=> "/assets/css/style.css" }

    %script{:src=>"http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"}
  %body
    %header.navbar.navbar-fixed-top
      .navbar-inner
        .container
          %a.brand{:href=>"/"} oahu
          %a.btn.btn-navbar{'data-toggle'=>'collapse', 'data-target'=>'.nav-collapse'}
            %span.icon-bar
            %span.icon-bar
            %span.icon-bar
          .nav-collapse
            %ul.nav.secondary-nav.pull-right
              %li.logged_in.dropdown{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected'}
                %a.dropdown-toggle{:href=>"#",  "data-toggle"=>"dropdown"}
                  %span.oahu_username{"data-oahu-bind"=>'name'}
                  %span.oahu_userpicture
                  %b.caret
                %ul.dropdown-menu
                  %li
                    %a.logout_btn{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected', "data-oahu-action"=>"disconnect", :href=>"#"} Logout
              %li.logged_out.login_status{"data-oahu-display"=>'disconnected'}
                %a.login_btn{:href=>'#', "data-oahu-display"=>'disconnected', "data-oahu-action"=>"connect", "data-oahu-provider"=>"facebook"} Login

            %ul.nav.pull-right
              %li
                %a{:href=>'#product'} Product
              %li
                %a{:href=>'#showcase'} Showcase
              %li
                %a{:href=>'#clients'} Clients
              %li
                %a{:href=>'#contact'} Contact
              %li
                %a{:href=>'#jobs'} Jobs
              %li
                %a.contact{:href=>'mailto:contact@oahu.fr'} contact@oahu.fr
    #page.container
      .hero-unit
        %h1
          Connect with your audience,
          %em anywhere
        %h2
          Oahu creates long term, meaningful relationships between you and your community
        %h3
          Oahu is an integrated marketing platform that enables you to build richer, more engaging campaigns.
      %section#product
        .page-header
          %h1 Product
        .row
          .span3
            %h2
              Optimized for engagement
            %p Our suite of apps and libraries lets content producers redefine the rules of marketing, by reducing time to market, ensuring highly integrated social components, and optimizing campaigns for engagement.
            %h4
              Spend less time setting up all the mundane steps of your campaign, and focus on creating value instead.

          .span3.offset1
            %h2 Simple to use
            %p 
              Publish our pre-built apps to instantly offer your fans Quizzes, Instant Wins, branded pages and more. You can build entire campaigns without a single line of code.
            %h4
              Oahu is built to grow with your campaign.
              %br
              We make it easy to publish and engage with your earliest content, and we follow you until you're launching your big bad main event. 

          .span3.offset1
            %h2 Full service
            %p We handle all the media, games mechanics, and user generated contents that make your campaigns richer and more compelling.
            %h4 Completely managed assets means your videos are encoded with the highest quality, your shares and tracking are correctly set up, and your deployment is quick and painless.

        .row
          .span3
            %h2 Rich & Realtime
            %p Leverage a robust set of rich realtime push components to create even more ambitious campaigns at a fraction of the time and cost.
            %h4 Your users are notified instantly when they win a badge, a goodie, when a friend offers them something, and just about anything you can think of.

          .span3.offset1
            %h2 Insightful
            %p With integrated metrics, Oahu shows you a precise breakdown of how your campaign’s doing, who’s playing, who’s sharing and much, much more.
            %h4 Define custom funnels of engagement to get detailed metrics on your users flow, what's making them share, what's engaging them.

          .span3.offset1
            %h2 Cross campaign
            %p Most importantly, We do all of this and more with an easy to use single sign-on, that authenticates your fans on all your platforms, enriches their profile across campaigns, allowing you to offer them precisely what makes them tick.
            %h4 The more you use Oahu, the more value your audience gains from it. Reward them for their engagement at a global scale, and make them ask for more !
      %section#testdrive{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected'}
        .page-header
          %h1 Test Oahu right here
        .row
          .span4
            %h2 Test out the main Oahu features
            %p
              Since you're connected to Oahu, here's a few simple features you can immediately test out.
              %br
              Many more are available.
            .connect
              %a.btn{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected', "data-oahu-action"=>'disconnect'} Disconnect
          .span4.logged_in{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected'}
            %h2
              Welcome,
              %span.username{"data-oahu-bind"=>'name'} 
            %p 
              %span.oahu_friendscount 0
              of your friends are using Oahu
            .share
              %a.btn{"data-oahu-action"=>"ui.share", "data-oahu-provider"=>"facebook"} Share your love
          .span4.logged_in{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected'}
            %h2 Your recent activity
            .activity{"data-oahu-bind"=>'activity'}



      %section
        .row
          #clients.span3.clearfix
            .page-header
              %h1 Clients
            %p.universal Universal
            %p.pathe Pathé
            %p.orange Orange

          #contact.span3.offset1
            .page-header
              %h1 Contact
            %h2
              Oahu is currently
              %br
              a private service.
            %p
              We plan on opening access to more clients in the near future. In the meantime, you can get more information by contacting us.
            .contact
              %a.btn.btn-large{:href=>'mailto:contact@oahu.fr'} contact@oahu.fr
          #jobs.span3.offset1
            .page-header
              %h1 Jobs
            %h2 We're  currently looking for : 
            %p
              %ul
                %li A front-end developer who knows CSS3, responsive design and Coffeescript perfectly.
                %li A product manager with a strong focus on detail and user experience
            .jobs
              %a.btn.btn-large{:href=>'mailto:jobs@oahu.fr'} jobs@oahu.fr


      %section#showcase
        .page-header
          %h1
            Showcase
            %small a sample of campaigns and sites using Oahu
        #carousel.carousel.row
          .carousel-inner
            .item
              .span8
                %img{:src=>'assets/img/screens/screen_01.jpg'}
              .span4
                %h2 American Pie 4

            .item
              .span8
                %img{:src=>'assets/img/screens/screen_02.jpg'}
              .span4
                %h2 Sur la piste du Marsupilami

            .item
              .span8
                %img{:src=>'assets/img/screens/screen_03.jpg'}
              .span4
                %h2 Battleship

            .item
              .span8
                %img{:src=>'assets/img/screens/screen_05.jpg'}
              .span4
                %h2 Pathé Films Portal

            .item
              .span8
                %img{:src=>'assets/img/screens/screen_06.jpg'}
              .span4
                %h2 Universal Pictures Film France Portail

            .item
              .span8
                %img{:src=>'assets/img/screens/screen_07.jpg'}
              .span4
                %h2 Le Prénom

            .item
              .span8
                %img{:src=>'assets/img/screens/screen_08.jpg'}
              .span4
                %h2 Twixt
          %a.carousel-control.left{:href=>'#carousel', "data-slide"=>'prev'}
          %a.carousel-control.right{:href=>'#carousel', "data-slide"=>'next'}

      %section#testdrive{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected'}
        .page-header
          %h1
            Testdrive
            %small Oahu as a user
        .row
          .span4
            %h2 Test out the main Oahu features
            %p
              Since you're connected to Oahu, here's a few simple features you can immediately test out.
              %br
              Many more are available.
            .connect
              %a.btn{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected', "data-oahu-action"=>'disconnect'} Disconnect
          .span4.logged_in{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected'}
            %h2
              Welcome,
              %span.username{"data-oahu-bind"=>'name'} 
            %p 
              %span.oahu_friendscount 0
              of your friends are using Oahu
            .share
              %a.btn{"data-oahu-action"=>"ui.share", "data-oahu-provider"=>"facebook"} Share your love
          .span4.logged_in{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected'}
            %h2 Your recent activity
            .activity{"data-oahu-bind"=>'activity'}



      :javascript
        document.createElement('section');
        document.createElement('header');
